[[File:Fundamentals_of_Biochemistry_fifth_edition.jpg|thumb|right|Cover of the fifth edition]]
'''''Fundamentals of Biochemistry: Life at the Molecular Level''''' is a biochemistry textbook written by [[Donald Voet]], [[Judith G. Voet]] and [[Charlotte W. Pratt]].<ref name="whatislife">{{cite web|url=http://www.whatislife.com/reviews/voet.htm|title=Reviews of books by Donald Voet, Judith Voet|last=Buehler |first=Lukas K. |date=January 2, 2000|publisher=Lukas K. Buehler |accessdate=18 January 2010}}</ref><ref name="TiBS">{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/S0968-0004(99)01447-4|last=Wood|first= E.J.|date=1 October 1999|title=Book review: Biochemistry in a nutshell - Fundamentals of Biochemistry by Donald Voet, Judith G. Voet and Charlotte W. Pratt|journal=Trends in Biochemical Sciences|volume=24|issue=10|pages= 409–410|accessdate=18 January 2010|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6TCV-3XH9GJD-C&_user=86629&_coverDate=10/01/1999&_rdoc=11&_fmt=high&_orig=browse&_srch=doc-info(%23toc%235180%231999%23999759989%23128531%23FLA%23display%23Volume)&_cdi=5180&_sort=d&_docanchor=&_ct=12&_acct=C000006878&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=86629&md5=44892cce3979f201de8c88e507483f3e}}</ref> Published by [[John Wiley & Sons]], it is a common undergraduate biochemistry textbook. 

As of 2016, the book has been published in 5 editions.<ref name="5th edition">{{cite book|title=Fundamentals of Biochemistry: Life at the Molecular Level|date=2016|publisher=[[John Wiley & Sons]]|isbn=1118918401}}</ref>

