{{List of members of the National Academy of Sciences/refcats}}

This is a list of [[manufacturers]] of [[solid-state drive]]s (SSD) for [[computer]]s and other [[electronic device]]s that require data storage. In this list those manufacturers that also produce [[hard disk drives]] and/or [[flash memory]] are identified. Additionally the type of memory used in their solid-state drives is noted. This list does not include manufacturers of only a component of the SSD, like the [[flash memory controller]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/6024/hynix-to-acquire-link-a-media-devices-lamd|title=Hynix to Acquire Link A Media Devices (LAMD)|last=Vättö|first=Kristian|access-date=2016-10-07}}</ref>

